# Privacy Policy for Study Lap

**Last updated:** [01/05/2026]

Welcome to Study Lap. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

### a. Personal Information

* Email address (via Firebase Authentication)
* User account details

### b. Usage Data

* App usage activity (features used, time spent)
* Progress data (coins, XP, streaks, leaderboard)

### c. Uploaded Content

* Files such as PDFs uploaded for summarization
* Messages sent in AI chat or guild chat

---

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

* Provide and maintain app functionality
* Authenticate users securely
* Improve app features and performance
* Personalize user experience
* Enable AI-based responses and learning features
* Manage leaderboards, rewards, and guild systems

---

## 3. Third-Party Services

We use trusted third-party services:

* Firebase Authentication (for login and identity)
* AI services (such as Google Gemini API for responses)

These services may collect and process data according to their own privacy policies.

